title: Seven presenter Daniels writes series with Rocky backdrop
text: Seven presenter Daniels writes series with Rocky backdrop Christina Ongley | 17th Oct 2015 7:00 AM Christina Ongley Senior Sub-editor I’m the daughter of retired small businesspeople who has moved about the country a lot with my parents’ ventures and, before that, my dad’s army career. I love making a home out of wherever I am, and I have a passion for getting to know people and telling their stories. I’ve been a journalist for more than 15 years and I haven’t met a person yet who doesn’t have an interesting story to tell.
